      },
      "source": "# Beyond RAG\n\n## Constructing Context Graphs and Multi Agent System hands on with AWS\n\n**Duration**: 90 minutes | **Cost**: ~$10-15 USD\n\n**Presenters** : \n\n- Monil Shah  , Senior Software Engineer, AWS\n- Vivek Ghatala, Senior Software Engineer, AWS\n\n### The Story\n\nAWS CapEx teams manage **$100B+ in infrastructure transactions** annually. Reconciling across Supply Chain Ordering, Invoice, General Ledger(GL), Subledger(SL), and Fixed Asset System(FS) is fragmented and decision context is lost every quarter.\n\nWe'll build an **AI-powered Metrics Assistant** that:\n\n1. **Retrieves** metric definitions with structure-preserving chunking (Module 1)\n2. **Reasons** over a context graph of decisions and relationships (Module 2)\n3. **Acts**  classifies risk, records decisions, captures email decisions (Module 3)\n\n### Prerequisites\n\n- AWS account with admin access\n- Bedrock model access enabled \n\n> **WARNING:** Run cells in order. Each cell builds on the previous one."
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "typeConfiguration": {
          "document": {
            "format": "MARKDOWN"
          }
        }
      },
      "source": "## Step 0: Install Dependencies & Configure Credentials"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
