          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": "  [0.535] (Decision) None: None\n  [0.532] (Policy) 90-Day PO Aging Threshold: New PO aging threshold approved to better reflect procurement timelines and redu\n    -> AFFECTS: False Positive Rate\n  [0.516] (Decision) PO Aging Threshold: Threshold defining when POs without receipts are flagged as overdue; changed fro\n    -> DEFINES: 90-Day Threshold\n    -> DEFINES: po_aging_not_invoiced\n    -> AFFECTS: PO to Receipt Matching\n  [0.477] (Policy) PO Aging Threshold: Threshold in days used to flag aged purchase orders; changed from 60 to 90 days \n    -> DEFINES: 90-Day Threshold\n    -> DEFINES: po_aging_not_invoiced\n    -> AFFECTS: PO to Receipt Matching\n  [0.452] (Decision) DEC-003: Changed PO aging not-invoiced threshold from 60 to 90 days to reduce false posit\n    -> AFFECTS: po_aging_not_invoiced\n    -> DEFINES: PO Aging Threshold\n    -> DECIDED: Sarah Chen\n\n[DECISIONS] Related Decisions:\n  [0.535] DEC-001: OFA to FASL+ Variance Threshold Set at $10K\n    Rationale: A $10K monthly variance threshold between OFA and FASL+ was established under GRC-001 to ensure reconciliation accuracy \n  [0.516] None: None\n    Rationale: None\n  [0.452] None: None\n    Rationale: None\n\n[SUCCESS] The graph returns WHY (decisions) alongside WHAT (current config)\n"
