        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": "-level coverage validation.\n[RESULT] Here is a comprehensive breakdown of the metrics that track PO aging for the **LLE category**, based on the knowledge base:\n\n---\n\n## 📊 PO Aging Metrics for the LLE Category\n\n### 1. `po_aging_not_invoiced`\n**Namespace:** `veritas_po_metrics`\n\n| Attribute | Detail |\n|---|---|\n| **Type** | COUNT, SUM |\n| **Value Column** | `po_amount` |\n| **Periods** | MTD, QTD |\n| **Dimensions** | entity, currency, cost_center |\n| **Key Filters** | `days_since_receipt > 90`, `invoice_status = PENDING` |\n| **Description** | Counts and sums POs that have been aging more than **90 days** without being invoiced. |\n\n> ⚠️ **Threshold Note (DEC-003):** The aging threshold was updated from **60 → 90 days** on 2024-10-15 by Sarah Chen (FBI CapEx Lead). The original 60-day threshold generated ~40% false positives during Q3 close. The 90-day threshold reduced false alerts by ~35%.\n\n---\n\n### 2. `po_total_spend`\n**Namespace:** `veritas_po_metrics`\n\n| Attribute | Detail |\n|---|---|\n| **Type** | SUM |\n| **Value Column** | `po_amount` |\n| **Breakdown Column** | `currency` |\n| **Period Column** | `po_received_at` |\n| **Periods** | MTD, QTD, YTD |\n| **Dimensions** | entity, region, cost_center |\n| **Key Filters** | `po_amount > 300`, `line_category IN [AHU, GENERATOR]` |\n| **Collections** | `po_number` |\n\n> This metric directly scopes to **LLE line categories** — specifically **AHU** and **GENERATOR** assets.\n\n---\n\n### 🏷️ LLE Category Scope — What's Included?\n\nPer **DEC-004** (2024-07-01, Michael Torres – Finance Director), the LLE category was expanded under a **FY2024 GAAP update** to include:\n- **AHU** (Air Handling Units) — original LLE asset type\n- **GENERATOR** — newly reclassified into LLE\n\nThis reclassification increased LLE transaction volume by **~15%**.\n\n---\n\n### 🔗 Supporting Coverage Metric\n\n| Metric | Namespace | Description |\n|---|---|---|\n| `afs_vs_ofa_coverage` | `lle_reconciliation` | Tracks the proportion of costs processed by AFS vs. total OFA balance for LLE (MTD, QTD, YTD). Helps confirm aging POs are being captured system-wide. |\n\n---\n\n**In summary**, the primary metric for tracking LLE PO aging is **`po_aging_not_invoiced`** (threshold: >90 days, status: PENDING), while **`po_total_spend`** provides spend-level visibility scoped directly to the LLE line categories (AHU, GENERATOR). The `afs_vs_ofa_coverage` metric in the `lle_reconciliation` namespace provides additional system-level coverage validation.\n\n"
